498
00:39:33,829 --> 00:39:35,581
Awak suruh saya pilih, jadi…

499
00:39:35,664 --> 00:39:37,166
Ya, betul.

500
00:39:37,249 --> 00:39:40,169
Bagus pilihan awak.

501
00:39:40,961 --> 00:39:43,923
Tapi, betullah awak tertekan, bukan?

502
00:39:45,091 --> 00:39:48,219
Tapi, saya faham.
