504
00:39:50,721 --> 00:39:53,391
Hujan turun selebat-lebatnya.

505
00:39:53,474 --> 00:39:55,017
Saya pula menangis.

506
00:39:55,101 --> 00:39:56,769
Mungkin awak ikutkan hati.

507
00:39:57,978 --> 00:40:00,398
Saya faham.

508
00:40:01,524 --> 00:40:03,025
