- Ya.

694
00:53:04,264 --> 00:53:06,266
GU SEUNG-JUN

695
00:53:29,372 --> 00:53:30,372
Helo.

696
00:53:30,707 --> 00:53:31,708
<i>Seung-jun.</i>

697
00:53:33,251 --> 00:53:34,294
Yoon Seri?

698
00:53:34,461 --> 00:53:37,839
Dah beberapa kali
saya cuba telefon Mr. Ri.

699
00:53:37,923 --> 00:53:38,923
